# TerminalDashboard Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and adjust values as needed.

# YGGDRASIL_ROOT – Root directory of the Yggdrasil ecosystem.
# The scanner will look for realm subdirectories (Asgard, Vanaheim, etc.)
# inside this directory.
# If not set, the scanner auto-detects by walking up from the package
# installation directory to find a parent directory named "Yggdrasil".
# YGGDRASIL_ROOT=/path/to/Yggdrasil
